ρωμένες</span></a></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-menu-item\"><a class=\"waves-effect waves-cyan \" href=\"https://mitroo.redcross.gr/index.php/dptadmin/missions/all\"><i class=\"material-icons\">important_devices</i><span class=\"menu-title\" >Όλες</span></a></li>\r\n        \r\n        <li class=\"navigation-header\"><a class=\"navigation-header-text\">ΑΙΤΗΣΕΙΣ ΑΠΟΣΤΟΛΩΝ  </a><i class=\"navigation-header-icon material-icons\">more_horiz</i></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-menu-item\"><a class=\"waves-effect waves-cyan \" href=\"https://mitroo.redcross.gr/index.php/dptadmin/shiftapplications/new\"><i class=\"material-icons\">account_box</i><span class=\"menu-title\" >Nέες</span></a></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-menu-item\"><a class=\"waves-effect waves-cyan \" href=\"https://mitroo.redcross.gr/index.php/dptadmin/shiftapplications/accepted\"><i class=\"material-icons\">account_box</i><span class=\"menu-title\" >Εγκεκριμένες</span></a></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-menu-item\"><a class=\"waves-effect waves-cyan \" href=\"https://mitroo.redcross.gr/index.php/dptadmin/shiftapplications/rejected\"><i class=\"material-icons\">account_box</i><span class=\"menu-title\" >Μη εγκεκριμένες</span></a></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-menu-item\"><a class=\"waves-effect waves-cyan \" href=\"https://mitroo.redcross.gr/index.php/dptadmin/shiftapplications/deputy\"><i class=\"material-icons\">account_box</i><span class=\"menu-title\" >Αναπλήρωση</span></a></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-menu-item\"><a class=\"waves-effect waves-cyan \" href=\"https://mitroo.redcross.gr/index.php/dptadmin/shiftapplications/all\"><i class=\"material-icons\">account_box</i><span class=\"menu-title\" >Όλες</span></a></li>\r\n\r\n                \r\n        \r\n        <li class=\"navigation-header\"><a class=\"navigation-header-text\">ΤΜΗΜΑ ΠΑΤΡΑ</a><i class=\"navigation-header-icon material-icons\">more_horiz</i></li>\r\n        <li class=\"navigation-me